      "eligibilityCriteria": {
        "eligibilityDescription_md": "\n1. The applicant must be a permanent resident of Uttarakhand.\n1. The applicant must possess a minimum of 40% disability. \n1. The applicant’s annual family income must not exceed ₹2,00,000 in urban areas and ₹1,60,000/- in rural areas.\n1. The applicant’s age must be between 18 and 50 years.\n\n",
